online\/2012\/09\/21\/umar-competes-with-abu-bakr\/","url_meta":{"origin":36177,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Competition: Umar tries to compete with Abu Bakr","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 21, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Umar ibn al-Khattab reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, ordered us to give charity and at the time I had some wealth. I said to myself, \u201cToday I will outdo Abu Bakr, if ever there were a day to outdo him.\u201d I went with half\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":43679,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/05\/14\/prophet-always-with-abu-bakr-umar\/","url_meta":{"origin":36177,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Caliphs: The Prophet always with Abu Bakr and Umar","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 14, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: Umar was placed upon his bier as the people surrounded him, supplicated for him, and performed the funeral prayer over him before he was taken away. I was there, and nothing else held my attention but a man putting his hand on my shoulder. It was Ali,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37549,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/12\/16\/salaam-bani-abu-bakr-umar\/","url_meta":{"origin":36177,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Ziyarah: Peace be on the Prophet, Abu Bakr, and Umar","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 16, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Nafi\u2019 reported: Ibn Umar, may Allah be pleased with him, when he arrived on his journey, he would enter the mosque of Medina and then go to the graves. Ibn Umar would say, \u201cPeace be upon you, O Messenger of Allah. Peace be upon you, O Abu Bakr. Peace be\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33356,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/09\/05\/ibn-sireen-degrades-abu-bakr\/","url_meta":{"origin":36177,"position":3},"title":"Ibn Sireen on Sahaba: Whoever degrades Abu Bakr and Umar","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 5, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ayyub reported: Muhammad ibn Sirin, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cI suspect that a man who denigrates Abu Bakr and Umar does not love the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3685 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u064a\u0651\u064f\u0648\u0628\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u064f\u062d\u064e\u0645\u0651\u064e\u062f\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0633\u0650\u064a\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0646\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11080,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/06\/ali-best-ummah-abu-bakr-umar\/","url_meta":{"origin":36177,"position":4},"title":"Ali on Caliphs: Best companions are Abu Bakr and Umar","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 6, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Juhayfah reported: Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cShall I not tell you about the best of this nation after its Prophet? It is Abu Bakr and Umar.\" Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 878 Grade\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u062c\u064f\u062d\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0641\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0644\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":39863,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/04\/21\/umar-fears\/","url_meta":{"origin":36177,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Tawhid: Umar afraid they take Allah\u2019s mercy for granted","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 21, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Bakr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cGo out and announce to the people that whoever testifies there is no God but Allah will surely enter Paradise.\u201d I went out and was met by Umar ibn al-Khattab. Umar said, \u201cReturn to the Messenger\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/36177","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaeli